  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was brilliant at it, and he did a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Vienna.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was one of the-- he was on the list.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, and how.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was-- and trouble is with him, he looked so Jewish that there was no way on earth that he could have.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was like Walter Mehring, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Dear Little Walter Mehring, who was about came up here on me, and he was, you know, the famous poet.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he wrote that beautiful poem, Phantom It was about a ship that some other gangsters had arranged.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were going to take-- to Africa, going to take a big group of people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was assigned to go down with them and wait there until we had to go outside of the harbor because-- you know, the harbor was always controlled.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the big fishing boat would come outside of the harbor, pick them up, and I would come back into town, and they would go on to safety in North Africa.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not so sure, because the Italians and the Germans were patrolling out there in the Mediterranean, too, you know, so it would have been a-- but anyway, the boat never came.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They'd been cheated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Later on we learned to tear money in half, you know, and give half now and half later.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But then we gave half before the whole thing, half the money, and of course, we never saw the boat or the gangsters.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Walter Mehring wrote this lovely poem called And finally it was getting daylight, and we had to leave because we couldn't be seen.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
